content:
Use the Record Rollup Definitions feature to streamline the aggregation of records from various objects or groups and to provide a consolidated view of your data.

The Record Rollup Definitions feature is available without installing the Financial Services Cloud managed package. By using an easy-to-use and intuitive UI, you can create record rollup definitions with just a few clicks.

Create Record Rollup Definitions More Easily
The Record Rollup Definitions feature allows you to aggregate records from various objects or groups and provide a consolidated view of your data.
This feature is available without installing the Financial Services Cloud managed package.
title: Streamlining Record Rollups in Salesforce
